txt.en: Return the crab meat, shells, and claws to Keteph

Keteph's continued success weighs upon him, and he makes another request of you regarding the crabs that walk the shores south and west of the outpost of Jax Phan창l. He asks that you gather meat, shells, and claws from the crabs and then return to him at Jax Phan창l.
'You will find the crabs along the shore, but I must ask that you are more careful not to destroy their claws. There is a great deal of flavour hidden within that I mean to use in my next creation.'

Keteph's culinary ascent continues. Demand for his stuffed crab shells has increased, and he asks yet again that you help him to acquire more materials for a new recipe.
'If I had a large enough stick, my friend, I would be driving customers away with swift swings. Alas, I have a mind meant for cooking and so my destiny is to be this outpost's chef.'
Return the crab meat, shells, and claws to Keteph
'With the right mix of herbs, spices, and other additives I will create a true feast fit for those loving this crusty critter. Thank you again for your assistance.'
